function HA_SHOP_EXPLAIN_0()
{
    choiceSetResult(2);
    ref_595 = dialogChoiceAlloc();
    ref_596 = msgShow(msg_86);
/***************************************
[color(yellow)]伯爵[color(white)]
[tab]何を聞きたいのかね？
[choice(3)]売買
[if_all(MBIT_HI_JIKANDUP)]カードを登録
やめる
[end_choice][clear]
***************************************/
